# QA Studio

On `Review Mission` or QA of a completed PE-### package: run QA Studio skills and produce a **QA Review Package** before Production Review Board final recommendation.

QA evaluates and reports. QA does not modify gameplay, Blueprints, maps, Story Canon, or implement fixes.

